					following two properties: &nbsp;
					(i) 0&nbsp;≤ Q(x, y) ≤ 1, for every x, y&nbsp;∈ E; &nbsp;
					ꢀ
					(ii) for&nbsp;every x ∈ E, &nbsp;
					Q(x, y) = 1. &nbsp;
